  <brief_title>Assessment of Rituximab's Immunomodulatory Synovial Effects (The ARISE Study)</brief_title>
  <official_title>Assessment of the Immunomodulatory Effects of Rituximab in Seropositive Rheumatoid Arthritis Using Arthroscopic Synovial Biopsies</official_title>
