  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      Using repeated arthroscopic biopsies of patients with rheumatoid arthritis, the researchers
      will assess changes in the immune response that occur as a result of treatment with
      rituximab.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
  <detailed_description>
    <textblock>
      Using repeated arthroscopic biopsies of patients with rheumatoid arthritis, the researchers
      will assess changes in the immune response that occur after treatment with rituximab.
    </textblock>
  </detailed_description>
